                        }
                    }
                }
            }  
            msgbox("Let me take a look at your Pok\edex{PAUSE 15}.{PAUSE 15}.{PAUSE 15}.
            
            It seems you haven't quite found all of
            the Alolan variants on Akala Isle
            just yet.
            
            I've heard Akala Isle has {COLOR RED}3 {COLOR DARK_GRAY}Alolan
