            {COLOR RED}Vulpix{COLOR DARK_GRAY}, {COLOR RED}Ninetales{COLOR DARK_GRAY}, {COLOR RED}Sandshrew{COLOR DARK_GRAY}, {COLOR RED}Sandslash{COLOR DARK_GRAY},
            {COLOR RED}Grimer{COLOR DARK_GRAY}, and {COLOR RED}Muk{COLOR DARK_GRAY}.

            Keep on searching and come back when
